30:09.100 --> 30:10.467
- Thank you.

30:10.500 --> 30:11.600
- Hmm.

30:11.633 --> 30:13.767
- Huh.

30:17.000 --> 30:19.367
This is really good.

30:19.400 --> 30:20.734
- Mm.

30:20.767 --> 30:23.467
Oh, my gosh.
Delicious.

30:23.500 --> 30:25.033
- Everything we've put
in our mouths

30:25.066 --> 30:26.667
