has been great.

30:26.700 --> 30:28.533
- Isn't he amazing?
all: Yeah.

30:28.567 --> 30:30.467
- I'd like to make a toast
to you guys.

30:30.500 --> 30:32.367
Here's to you
and your families.

30:32.400 --> 30:33.433
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

30:33.467 --> 30:35.000
- They loved your dinner.

30:35.033 --> 30:36.400
- Even though it wasn't
on his preference sheet.

30:36.433 --> 30:38.033
- That could have been
a disaster.

