- Okay.

40:00.533 --> 40:02.166
- Good job, Rhylee.

40:02.200 --> 40:04.066
- So ten minutes?
- Yeah, not even.

40:04.100 --> 40:05.734
- I think they're
freshening up.

40:05.767 --> 40:07.166
- I'm sorry I wasn't
communicating with you

40:07.200 --> 40:08.567
