that's fine.

40:48.100 --> 40:49.600
- I did and you didn't--
- But if I feel--okay, sorry.

40:49.633 --> 40:51.300
And I'm telling you,
if I feel comfortable,

40:51.333 --> 40:52.600
then I feel comfortable,
all right.

40:52.633 --> 40:54.333
Let's talk about this later
because I've got--

40:54.367 --> 40:56.033
we've got sh-- to do.
- Okay.

40:56.066 --> 40:57.467
Well, I understand
it's another opinion.

40:57.500 --> 40:59.233
- You need to--you need to--
- I understand--

40:59.266 --> 41:00.533
I understand it's another
opinion. I'm not--

41:00.567 --> 41:02.100
- Yeah, I understand it's a--
I'm sorry.

41:02.133 --> 41:03.433
Go ahead and tell me
to ----ing, what?

41:03.467 --> 41:05.066
- No, you need to--
I'm not telling you to--

41:05.100 --> 41:06.400
- You just did.
[chuckles]

41:06.433 --> 41:08.300
- Dude, all right,
go to the--go--let's...

41:08.333 --> 41:10.100
- Yes, sir. Yes, sir.
- You go sort the

41:10.133 --> 41:12.033
beach club out.
Oh, (BLEEP).

