There's no reasoning
with Rhylee.

41:13.333 --> 41:15.300
She's a strong-minded woman.
I respect that.

41:15.333 --> 41:17.300
I respect that she doesn't want
to be disrespected

41:17.333 --> 41:20.200
at the same time, but listen
here, love, enough's enough.

41:20.233 --> 41:22.166
Now, you're disrespecting me.

41:24.033 --> 41:25.300
- I was Japanese
in another life.

41:25.333 --> 41:27.266
- I'm feeling that.
I can tell.

41:27.300 --> 41:28.266
Thank you.

