- Hi.
- Hey!

41:33.467 --> 41:35.033
- Oh, my God.
- Wow, look at this.

41:35.066 --> 41:37.266
- Ponzu chicken
and a sesame beef.

41:37.300 --> 41:38.433
- This guy.
- Yes.

41:38.467 --> 41:40.066
Oh, my goodness!

41:40.100 --> 41:42.633
Salmon, tuna, yum.

41:42.667 --> 41:45.300
- Oh, my God,
these are ridiculous.

41:45.333 --> 41:47.467
- How is everything so far?
- Amazing.

41:47.500 --> 41:49.166
- Wow.

41:49.200 --> 41:50.533
- Chandler, what's-her-name,
Rhylee,

41:50.567 --> 41:52.233
she's just not
cooperating well, dude.

41:52.266 --> 41:54.033
